'''穆罕默德佈道周年紀念日'''（Eid al-Ghadeer）是紀念先知[[穆罕默德|穆罕默德]]在[[伊斯蘭曆|伊斯蘭曆]]十年[[都爾黑哲月|都爾黑哲月]]十八日在[[拉比谷乾谷|拉比谷乾谷]]（Ghadir Khumm）作最後一次佈道的節日<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = The Office of Ayatollah Sheikh Mohammad Hussein AlAnsari | title = Eid al-Ghadeer | url = http://www.alansaree.info/index.php/library/43-sig-religious-events/64-eid-ghadeer | accessdate = 2009-09-15 }}</ref>。什葉派教徒會慶祝穆罕默德佈道周年紀念日<ref>{{cite web|language=en |publisher=Oneummah.net |title=Eid-ul-Ghadeer |url=http://www.oneummah.net/understand/eid.htm |accessdate=2009-09-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721081846/http://www.oneummah.net/understand/eid.htm |archivedate=2011-07-21 }}</ref>，並以此作為確立[[阿里·本·阿比·塔利卜|阿里·本·阿比·塔利卜]]是[[穆罕默德繼承者|穆罕默德繼承者]]的身份<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Aswat al-Iraq | title = 280 couples marry in public ceremony | url = http://en.aswataliraq.info/?p=64577 | date = 2007-12-31 | accessdate = 2009-09-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305042615/http://en.aswataliraq.info/?p=64577 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。遜尼派對此並無異議，但不會在該天慶祝，遜尼派教徒認為只有[[開齋節|開齋節]]及[[古爾邦節|古爾邦節]]才值得慶祝。

